author: By JOCELYN NOVECK AP National Writer
title: Couples in quarantine: Stress, anxiety, fear of the unknown
description: The 60-something husband works in the food industry and still insists upon leaving every day for work, saying he needs to keep his business afloat. His frightened wife desperately wants him to stay home.
